------------------------------------------
Deathrun_Trilogy by -[Element]- (a.k.a elementa1)
------------------------------------------

This map has 12 traps. Easy to hard difficulty.

It is somewhat short, but has great gameplay.

Not much else to say. 

Also, the buttons respawn every 10 seconds,
accept the breakable floors.

In the T side, which can't be seen by the ct's, 
has a ramp at end just incase they fall behind.

There are 4 T spawns and 20 CT spawns
